Retail Sales Associate<br>
<br>
As Australia's leading retailer of mobile device accessories and repairs, Happytel Retail Group has recently expanded in America! With over 70 stores and 20 years of experience, we are looking for friendly, motivated and energetic Retail Sales Associate to redefine the way customers view accessories and repairs.This gives us an great new opportunity to add to the Happytel family. If you have an interest for the latest innovative and dynamic gadgets, love working in a culture that aims for happiness or just want to gain some valuable career experience, then look no further!<br>
<br>
We are looking for 3 New Part Time Retail Associates in three of our stores.<br>
- Arrowhead Towne Centre (1 Position)<br>
- Scottsdale Fashion Square (1 Position)<br>
- Chandler Fashion Center (1 Position)<br>
<br>
Key Duties and Responsibilities:<br>
- Provide excellent customer service<br>
- Demonstrate products and show customers how to maximize their features<br>
- Provide basic smartphone repair service<br>
- Assist the Manager in the day to day operations of the store<br>
- Process orders in person and over the phone<br>
- Maintain good visual merchandising and store presentation<br>
<br>
To be considered for this you will have:<br>
- A passion for customer service and sales achievement<br>
- Be flexible to work 7-day rotating roster (including weekends and late night trade)<br>
- Previous retail experience is preferred but not essential<br>
- The ability to work well in a team focused and fast paced environment<br>
- Strong interpersonal and communication skills<br>
- Reliable and dedicated to the job<br>
<br>
What we can offer you:<br>
- An attractive remuneration package<br>
- Training and development, and career progression opportunities.<br>
- Staff Discounts.<br>
- A friendly team culture that revolves around happiness.<br>
<br>
Join a fun and exciting company with a big bright future and, who is recognized as the leader in the industry!<br>
<br>
If you're excited by this job opportunity and would like to kick start your career in retail, APPLY NOW.<br>
<br>
If you would like to find out more of our company please visit:<br>
<a href="http://us.happytel.com/" rel="nofollow">http://us.happytel.com/</a>    </section>

